description: A large, cylindrical, reactor-powered freighter that comes standard with two D2O tanks. The Ocelot gained minor notoriety in 2078 when an unskilled pilot dragged one across the surface of 1036 Ganymed after miscalculating a simple maneuver. Now folks say the ship only has eight lives left.
